name: ExtensionManufacturedItemDefinition
title: Cross-version Extension `R5.ManufacturedItemDefinition` for use in FHIR R4
description: This cross-version extension represents the FHIR R5 element `ManufacturedItemDefinition` for use in FHIR R4.
purpose:
This extension is part of the cross-version definitions generated to enable use of the
element `ManufacturedItemDefinition` as defined in FHIR R5
in FHIR R4.

The source element is defined as:
`ManufacturedItemDefinition` 0..* `ManufacturedItemDefinition`

Across FHIR versions, the element set has been mapped as:
*  R5: `ManufacturedItemDefinition` 0..* `ManufacturedItemDefinition`

Following are the generation technical comments:
FHIR R5 Resource `ManufacturedItemDefinition` is representable via FHIR R4 Resource `Basic`.
Element `ManufacturedItemDefinition` is not mapped to FHIR R4, since FHIR R5 `ManufacturedItemDefinition` is not mapped.
